WEBVTT


00:00:00.440 --> 00:00:01.200
Hi everyone,

00:00:01.200 --> 00:00:02.440
my name is M. Drinko.

00:00:02.440 --> 00:00:03.480
I'm a dairy farmer

00:00:03.480 --> 00:00:06.000
and I also do at the Drinko Dairy on TikTok.

00:00:06.000 --> 00:00:07.800
I just like to take 2 minutes to talk to you

00:00:07.800 --> 00:00:09.580
about mental health and farming.

00:00:09.720 --> 00:00:11.920
Agriculture has one of the highest rates of suicide

00:00:11.920 --> 00:00:14.640
in the UK. It is the biggest killer of farmers,

00:00:14.640 --> 00:00:17.500
which is absolutely heartbreaking and needs to change.

00:00:18.000 --> 00:00:19.720
The next time you're at the pub with your mates

00:00:19.720 --> 00:00:20.520
and someone asks

00:00:20.520 --> 00:00:21.360
are you okay?

00:00:21.360 --> 00:00:22.880
It is perfectly fine to say,

00:00:22.880 --> 00:00:23.240
you know what?

00:00:23.240 --> 00:00:25.280
No, I'm not feeling 100% today.

00:00:25.280 --> 00:00:27.380
Because it's okay not to be. Okay.

00:00:27.480 --> 00:00:29.000
We need to do something about this.

00:00:29.000 --> 00:00:30.200
And the way to do that

00:00:30.200 --> 00:00:32.000
is bring about new thinking of this.

00:00:32.000 --> 00:00:34.420
So let's do just that and let's get talking.
